 Emzo is a prolific producer and song writer. Born and raised in Benin city, Edo state he started out as a back up vocalist and studio assistant before applying himself and learning the tricks and craftsmanship of producing and audio engineering. He has worked with several industry heavyweights such as Jaywon, Mr Eazi, Olamide, Yemi Alade to name a few. ‘PURPLE CLIMAX‘ is his first project and according to the multi-talented producer and singer there are so many other song releases lined up for the last two quarters of the year, but before then, enjoy this beautiful piece he titles “IN THE RAIN“. Listen!!! https://tooxclusive.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Emzo-In-The-Rain.mp3 DOWNLOAD MP3 The post Emzo – “In The Rain” appeared first on tooXclusive. Source: TooXclusiv